sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Claude
    participant SessionHook as SessionStart Hook
    participant PromptHook as UserPromptSubmit Hook
    participant PreHook as PreToolUse Hook
    participant Command as Command Execution
    participant PostHook as PostToolUse Hook
    participant StopHook as Stop Hook

    User->>Claude: Start session
    Claude->>SessionHook: Fire once per session
    SessionHook-->>Claude: Inject ARCKIT_VERSION + detect projects/
    
    User->>Claude: /arckit:command
    Claude->>PromptHook: Fire before command starts
    PromptHook->>PromptHook: Scan projects/, extract metadata
    PromptHook-->>Claude: additionalContext (project inventory)
    
    Claude->>Command: Execute with context
    Command->>PreHook: Attempt Write tool
    PreHook->>PreHook: Validate filename, route to subdirectory
    PreHook-->>Command: Corrected filename or error
    
    Command->>Command: Generate document
    Command->>PostHook: File written
    PostHook->>PostHook: Update docs/manifest.json
    PostHook-->>Command: Manifest updated
    
    alt Wardley Map Command
        Command->>StopHook: Command completes
        StopHook->>StopHook: Validate OWM syntax
        StopHook-->>Claude: Block or allow completion
    end
